%25BB%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%2589%2580%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A7%258B%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2582%2589%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0WPETiIbFLwQu3AXIvKBDx_J-tz8V8m-W-lkY8aagA6hppW3gFbOxXiy0&h=76d3638f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92-721-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%88%87%E5%BF%83%E8%85%B9%E7%9D%87%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%BD%AE%E6%88%BF%E5%A4%96-%E9%A6%AE%E7%A8%8B%E6%B7%91%E5%84%80%E5%8E%BB%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80%E7%9C%8B%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%A7%8B%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A/?fbclid=IwAR0WPETiIbFLwQu3AXIvKBDx_J-tz8V8m-W-lkY8aagA6hppW3gFbOxXiy0</a><br />\n<br />\n報道引述三名知情人士指，在元朗 721 襲擊事件當晚，林鄭與數名心腹在禮賓府，他們為了保安理由，將電話都放在房間外。各人在房內收看主要電視台的新聞報道，觀察著中聯辦及上環一帶的示威情況，但就沒有留意網媒、社交平台上正廣傳的元朗襲擊事件。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，政策創新與統籌辦事處總監馮程淑儀踏出房間去洗手間，他們才知悉元朗的情況。馮程淑儀當時在 WhatsApp 群組收到一連串有關元朗的信息後，仍然對事件抱有疑惑。她向同事發短訊指元朗站理應已關閉，質疑這些群組廣傳的影片是否「假新聞」<br />\n<br />\n原來我哋怪錯咗777<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPR佬你作都作好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都再次證明港共CARE中聯辦棟死物多過香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81abcbe386b5a6824b91289d2a6d95d7fdae20f","tid":2195010,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c